          <p>Liverpool has one of the highest concentrations of Victorian and Edwardian housing in England. Many of these properties have gravity-fed systems, back boilers, chimneys used as flue routes and pipework configurations that differ significantly from modern builds. Our engineers have 30 years experience working specifically in Liverpool's housing stock. We know which problems to anticipate and how to solve them efficiently. See <a href="https://www.hse.gov.uk/gas/domestic/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">HSE domestic gas safety guidance</a> for further information on gas installation safety requirements.</p>
