          <p>Boiler output is measured in kilowatts (kW). A small flat or 1 to 2 bed home typically needs a 24 to 28kW combi boiler. A 3 bed home needs 28 to 32kW and larger properties with multiple bathrooms need 32 to 40kW or a system boiler setup. We calculate the correct size at the free survey based on your property size, number of radiators and hot water demand. Fitting an incorrectly sized boiler is one of the most common and costly mistakes in boiler installations.</p>
